ctrl + alt + l  >> auto format code
ctrl + shift + f10  >> run actually opened code
ctrl + k  >> git commit
ctrl + shift + k  >> git push to repo
ctrl + t  >> update project from git
ctrl + /  > comment/uncomment part of code
shift + del  > delete line where you have cursor
tab  >> indent code to the right
shift + tab  << indent code to the left
alt + j  >> multi cursor functionality
ctrl + d  >> copy line where cursor is
ctrl + shift + u  >> capitalize selected fragment
ctrl + p  >> hint for input arguments to any function
"""<enter>"""  >> auto documentation for function with properly typed arguments
cursor at unresolved reference & alt+enter >> import unresolved reference from libs

pip3 commands:
pip3 install -r ./App/requirements.txt

